<section class="panel">
  <h2>About This Portfolio</h2>
  <p>
    This project is the Node A02 view engine refactor, built on top of the A01
    launchpad. It uses EJS as a server-side view engine for rendering all HTML
    pages, with two layout templates and shared partials.
  </p>
  <p>
    Project data is loaded from a JSON file on the server and rendered directly
    into the page — no client-side fetching required.
  </p>
</section>
